com.tsgrp.migration.queue

Class JdbcMigrationQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.queue.AbstractMigrationQueue
      • com.tsgrp.migration.queue.JdbcMigrationQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationQueue

    public class JdbcMigrationQueue
extends AbstractMigrationQueue
    The JDBC migration queue serves as a ledger that accounts for all objects moved from the source to the target. It writes to a table containing columns utilized to track the status of a MigrationNode as it is queued, processed, and completed.
